The paper discusses the use of RGB-D sensors in robotics and augmented reality, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses 3D scene reconstruction and optimization techniques, which are relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the estimation of ego-motion and camera trajectory, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and control systems (cs.SY).
